00:06:35.600 --> 00:06:38.410 align:middle line:84%
>> There are common themes
that run through all of these

00:06:38.410 --> 00:06:39.550 align:middle line:90%
stories.

00:06:39.550 --> 00:06:42.610 align:middle line:10%
One of those themes
is that civilization

00:06:42.610 --> 00:06:44.980 align:middle line:10%
is cyclic rather than linear.

00:06:44.980 --> 00:06:48.970 align:middle line:84%
That there have been previous
cycles of civilization

00:06:48.970 --> 00:06:52.760 align:middle line:84%
that have lasted for
approximately 5,000 years.

00:06:52.760 --> 00:06:55.210 align:middle line:84%
Something happens, those
cycles come to an end,

00:06:55.210 --> 00:06:56.930 align:middle line:90%
a new cycle begins.

00:06:56.930 --> 00:06:58.780 align:middle line:84%
This is where it gets
really interesting.

00:06:58.780 --> 00:07:01.900 align:middle line:84%
Because even though
the cycles change,

00:07:01.900 --> 00:07:05.410 align:middle line:84%
there appears to be a
continuity of knowledge,

00:07:05.410 --> 00:07:09.280 align:middle line:84%
a continuity of wisdom when
