00:08:08.260 --> 00:08:10.660 align:middle line:84%
have been taught that
civilization began in,

00:08:10.660 --> 00:08:12.220 align:middle line:90%
5,500 years ago.

00:08:12.220 --> 00:08:16.090 align:middle line:84%
Now, new discoveries are
revealing the remnants

00:08:16.090 --> 00:08:20.660 align:middle line:84%
of ancient civilizations that
predate that 5,000 years many,

00:08:20.660 --> 00:08:23.185 align:middle line:90%
many times.

00:08:23.185 --> 00:08:25.560 align:middle line:10%
>> One of the things that's
echoed in the ancient stories

00:08:25.560 --> 00:08:28.080 align:middle line:10%
around the world, whether or
not it's Plato talking about

00:08:28.080 --> 00:08:31.260 align:middle line:10%
Atlantis or the ancient
Egyptians and the Temple

00:08:31.260 --> 00:08:35.070 align:middle line:10%
of Sais is that we find that
they discuss how these events

00:08:35.070 --> 00:08:37.150 align:middle line:10%
have come in many
different ways.

00:08:37.150 --> 00:08:38.909 align:middle line:84%
They discuss how
the civilizations

00:08:38.909 --> 00:08:42.179 align:middle line:84%
have been destroyed from
periods of great flooding,

00:08:42.179 --> 00:08:45.390 align:middle line:90%
but also extreme heat and fire.

00:08:45.390 --> 00:08:47.730 align:middle line:84%
So it's not just
about one thing,

00:08:47.730 --> 00:08:50.760 align:middle line:84%
it's about a totality of all
of these different catastrophic

00:08:50.760 --> 00:08:53.160 align:middle line:84%
events that have led
to the disappearance

00:08:53.160 --> 00:08:56.850 align:middle line:84%
and destruction of these
predeluvian civilizations.

00:08:56.850 --> 00:08:59.070 align:middle line:84%
And the way that we have
the telltale evidence

00:08:59.070 --> 00:09:01.410 align:middle line:84%
is that a lot of these
ancient megalithic structures

00:09:01.410 --> 00:09:02.970 align:middle line:84%
from the predeluvian
civilizations

00:09:02.970 --> 00:09:06.330 align:middle line:84%
they left behind is that we find
what's known as vitrification

00:09:06.330 --> 00:09:07.780 align:middle line:90%
on the surface.

00:09:07.780 --> 00:09:10.530 align:middle line:84%
Whether or not it's
Egypt or Peru or Turkey.

00:09:10.530 --> 00:09:13.230 align:middle line:84%
And what that means is
that those granite blocks

00:09:13.230 --> 00:09:15.540 align:middle line:84%
in the quartz that
was in them literally

00:09:15.540 --> 00:09:20.178 align:middle line:84%
melted from such an extreme heat
event that in order to do that,

00:09:20.178 --> 00:09:22.470 align:middle line:84%
you have to have temperatures
on the surface that would

00:09:22.470 --> 00:09:27.090 align:middle line:90%
have exceeded 2,000 degrees.

00:09:27.090 --> 00:09:31.290 align:middle line:84%
>> Researchers and mythological
heroes on a journey have long

00:09:31.290 --> 00:09:34.770 align:middle line:84%
looked to the sky for answers
to explain what happened

00:09:34.770 --> 00:09:36.300 align:middle line:90%
in the past.

00:09:36.300 --> 00:09:39.660 align:middle line:84%
